<p>英 /kəm'pæʃn/    美 /kəm'pæʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 怜悯；同情：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was shocked by his <strong>lack of compassion</strong>.
他如此缺乏同情心，让我很震惊。</p></div></div>